ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend this class to a fellow student, as the class is both broad and allows you to specialize your interests to the class, especially as graduate students.
I would recommend PSYCH 557 to another classmate. I thought the course material was very interesting and useful for people in many branches of psychology, and even outside of psychology.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This class deepened my understanding of a topic that will potentially be in my research in the future, so this course definitely deepened my understanding of this topic and whetted my interest in exploring this construct within relationships to a greater degree than would have occurred otherwise.
This course deepened my knowledge of psychology by giving a fuller and more up-to-date understanding of questions that I had only somewhat peripherally understood before
